metadata.name: THE PUDGY !RIOT ORDER
metadata.description:
A long time ago during the Pudgy Penguin Ice Age, a few friendly penguins danced and !Riot'ed around happily in the freezing tundra and discovered a hidden prophecy in a cave. It contained a hidden message that was revealed to them by the unknown ... about a secret Pudgy !RIOT Order ... that will rise one day. 

!RIOT and the doors to the order will be revealed.
